_G_e_n_e_r_a_l_i_z_e_d _B_o_o_s_t_e_d _R_e_g_r_e_s_s_i_o_n _M_o_d_e_l_s

_D_e_s_c_r_i_p_t_i_o_n:

     This package implements extensions to Freund and Schapire's
     AdaBoost algorithm and J. Friedman's gradient boosting machine.
     Includes regression methods for least squares, absolute loss,
     logistic, Poisson, Cox proportional hazards partial likelihood,
     and AdaBoost exponential loss.

_D_e_t_a_i_l_s:


